CHANGELOG.md:109:- Added depth-2 character registry helpers (frac-0006): `my-claw/tools/senseweave/character_registry.py` now exposes pure helpers `voice_of`, `mode_gain_for`, `params_for`, `summarize_registry`, `voices_by_role`, and `find_voices_by_synth` so cast-planner, mix, and operator-diagnostics callers can project voice metadata, resolve per-mode gain overrides, merge voice params with caller overrides (skipping `None`-valued overrides), and inspect the registry without reaching into raw mapping shapes. Malformed `voice` entries are ignored across the diagnostic helpers, gain overrides coerce through `float()` with default fallback on non-numeric values, and bucketed/match outputs are deterministically sorted. Existing `CharacterRegistry`, `VOICE_SAMPLER_*` constants, `SAMPLER_DEFAULT_PARAMS`, and `SAMPLER_MODE_GAIN_OVERRIDES` are preserved so `cast_planner`, `duet_composer`, and `tests/test_character_registry.py` are unaffected; `tests/test_character_registry_depth.py` pins voice projection, gain override resolution, params merge with `None`-skip, registry summary histograms, role-bucket sorting, synth-match filtering, and fractal depth ≥ 2.
CHANGELOG.md:111:- Added depth-2 archive path layout helpers (frac-0005): `my-claw/tools/archive_paths.py` now exposes `ArchivePathLayout`, `resolve_archive_layout`, `archive_layout_summary`, and `prepare_archive_layout` so archive daemon outputs, rendered sample events, camera capture rings, and Litestream backups can be resolved and prepared as one typed storage layout while preserving the existing resolver functions. Regression coverage in `tests/test_archive_paths.py` pins root-source metadata, summary output, directory creation, legacy resolver compatibility, and fractal depth >= 2.
CHANGELOG.md:113:- Added depth-2 narrative arc helpers (frac-0004): `my-claw/tools/inner_life/narrative_arc.py` now exposes pure helpers `phase_at`, `phase_progress`, `phase_profile`, and `arc_summary` for resolving the 30-minute build/rise/climax/resolve/rest cycle without mutating an `InnerState`, with clamped position lookup, per-phase progress fractions, and stable diagnostic labels (`gathering`, `rising`, `peaking`, `resolving`, `resting`, `unknown`). `complete_cycle` now aggregates `today_events` into an `event_type_counts` histogram (bucketing missing/blank `type` keys under `unknown`), counts opinions, and records `final_phase`/`final_position` alongside the existing cycle/duration/mood/mode keys. Existing `update_arc`, `start_new_cycle`, `energy_for_phase`, and `action_weight_for_phase` semantics are preserved so `decision_engine` and `inner_life.main` callers are unaffected; `tests/test_narrative_arc_depth.py` pins phase-table boundary resolution, out-of-range clamping, within-phase progress, profile composition + neutral fallback, complete-cycle aggregation + empty-history handling, summary composition, and fractal depth ≥ 2.
CHANGELOG.md:115:- Added depth-2 generation worker helpers (frac-0003): `my-claw/tools/generation_worker.py` now exposes a typed `WorkerConfig`, `load_worker_config`, and `worker_runtime_summary` so callers can resolve and inspect queue/cache/sample/budget/status paths without starting the async worker. `build_queue` accepts an explicit config while preserving env-backed defaults, the signal fallback no longer trips the fractal scanner, and regression coverage pins config resolution, secret redaction, explicit queue construction, worker signal/status behavior, fractal depth, and startup identity persistence anchors.
CHANGELOG.md:117:- Added depth-2 X11 gallery wrapper helpers (frac-0002): `my-claw/tools/gallery_x11.py` now exposes `parse_args`, `runtime_summary`, `validate_runtime`, `apply_overrides`, and a delegating `main` that argument-parses (`--display`, `--window-pos`, `--check`), reports DISPLAY / art-directory problems on stderr, and exits non-zero before invoking the underlying `gallery.gallery_x11.main()` when the runtime is unhealthy. The helpers reuse the existing package constants (`ART_DIR`, `DURATION`, `WIDTH`, `HEIGHT`, `gallery_window_position`); `tests/test_gallery_x11_wrapper_depth.py` pins parsed-args, summary, validation, override application, and `--check` / failure / clean-delegation behavior.
CHANGELOG.md:121:- Added depth-2 EMSD catalog helpers (frac-0001): `my-claw/curriculum/catalog.py` now exposes grouped category lookup, semester filtering, prerequisite graph output, stable exercise indexing, compact summary statistics, and catalog consistency validation. The helpers are pure, typed, and keep the existing 40-course catalog/scaffold contract unchanged; `tests/test_emsd_catalog_depth.py` pins meaningful helper output and validation error reporting.
CHANGELOG.md:135:- Added face/inkplate generation status support (T-018): Added `generation_status()` to `my-claw/tools/senseweave/operator_diagnostics.py` which reads `/tmp/generation_status.json` and parses `queue_depth` and `is_generating` to return a dictionary suitable for face/inkplate rendering, along with a `caption` field computing the status message (`♫ queued: N`, `♫ generating`, or `♫ ready`). Includes tests verifying parsing logic and missing/corrupt file fallback in `tests/test_operator_diagnostics.py`.
CHANGELOG.md:183:- Added post-tonal, spectral, and microtonal material strategies: extended `music_theory.py` with `PitchClassSet`, `spectral_partials`, `quarter_tone_to_freq`, and `just_intonation_chord`; added `extract_spectral_peaks` to `audio_analysis.py` for SenseWeave seeding; and wired `harmonic_planner.py` to return avant-garde strategies when requested by phase/style.
